### Important Learnings
- INNER JOIN returns matching rows only
- LEFT JOIN keeps all rows from the left table
- NULL values indicate missing matches
- GROUP BY creates separate groups for aggregation
- Aggregate functions work inside groups
- Multiple correct SQL solutions can exist for same problem

